headline.main: Acosta Scores in 69th, FC Dallas Beats LA Galaxy 2-1
headline.print_headline: Acosta Scores in 69th, FC Dallas Beats LA Galaxy 2-1

lead_paragraph: Kellyn Acosta scored in the 69th minute and FC Dallas beat the Los Angeles Galaxy 2-1 in a Major League Soccer opener Saturday.
